== 個人生活 ==
潘攀的丈夫是國家隊的隊友[[徐晨|徐晨]]。她在左脚腕上纹有“panc”的[[纹身|纹身]]，是她和徐晨名字的缩写<ref>{{cite news|title=徐晨/潘攀：女追男九年成正果 纪念日浪漫求婚|url=http://sports.sohu.com/20110814/n316287160.shtml|newspaper=搜狐体育|date=2011-08-14|accessdate=2012-09-18|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124002727/https://sports.sohu.com/20110814/n316287160.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。二人在2014年6月3日結婚<ref>{{cite news|title=国羽情侣徐晨潘攀婚礼 谌龙王适娴等人到场|url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/o/2014-06-03/16557192762.shtml|newspaper=新浪体育|date=2014-06-03|accessdate=2014-09-28|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209004553/http://sports.sina.com.cn/o/2014-06-03/16557192762.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

